p11
aVBut let me suggest a fourth one:
p12
aVmathematics.
p13
aVDid you know that Paris has more mathematicians
p14
aVthan any other city in the world?
p15
aVAnd more streets with mathematicians' names, too.
p16
aVAnd if you look at the statistics of the Fields Medal,
p17
